agency_name: Department of Workforce Development and Advancement
series_description: This series documents the number of employees and total wages by geographical area and business industry that are submitted by employers to the United States Department of Labor, Bureau of Labor Statistics. This series may include, but is not limited to: quarterly reports.

agency_name: Department of Workforce Development and Advancement
series_description: This series documents industry and business information of employers conducting business in the Commonwealth that is reported to the United States Department of Labor, Bureau of Labor Statistics. This series may include, but is not limited to: Industry Verification Form BLS 3023.

agency_name: Department of Workforce Development and Advancement
series_description: This series documents quarterly employment and wage data employers that have multiple locations. This series may but is not limited to: Multiple Worksite Report BLS 3020-MWR.

agency_name: Department of Workforce Development and Advancement
series_description: This series documents occupational, employment, and wage data submitted by employers to the United States Department of Labor, Bureau of Labor Statistics and used to verify of previously submitted employer data including Standard Occupational Classification(SOC) codes. This series may include, but is not limited to: surveys.
